# Implementation Plan — Employee System Overhaul

A complete redesign of the employee management system covering frontend form redesign, space management, responsibility-salary engine, and leave management.

---

## 1. Auto Employee ID Generation

### Backend
- Add [generate_employee_id](file:///home/shivnk/.gemini/antigravity/playground/deep-helix/Ai-school/Backend/src/repository/postgres.rs#804-811) in [repository/postgres.rs](file:///home/shivnk/.gemini/antigravity/playground/deep-helix/Ai-school/Backend/src/repository/postgres.rs) using sequence: `E` + zero-padded counter → `E0001`, `E0002`, etc.
- `POST /api/employees/:schoolId/employees` returns `{ success, employee: { employeeId, ... } }` — already partially done; fix ID format.

### Frontend ([employeeform.jsx](file:///home/shivnk/.gemini/antigravity/playground/deep-helix/Ai-school/Vidhyam/src/features/employees/components/employeeform.jsx))
- On successful submit → show dialog/modal with generated Employee ID
- Employee type dropdown: **Teacher, Peon, Principal, Admin, Other**

