## 2. Separate Form Sections

### 2a. Personal Info
Fields: Name, Father Name, Mother Name, DOB, Age (auto-calc from DOB), Gender, Category (General/OBC/SC/ST), Blood Group, Employee Type (dropdown)

### 2b. Experience Section (New — `EmployeeExperience` table)
- **Is Fresher** checkbox
- If not fresher, add entries (multiple):
  - Organization Name, Location, Position/Profile Type, Post Type (dropdown: Permanent/Contractual/Part-Time/Guest)
  - Join Month & Year, End Date (or "Current" checkbox)
  - Achievement Description, Previous Employee ID, Experience Letter Image URL
- Backend: `employee_experience` table (JSONB or relational)

### 2c. Education Section (New — `EmployeeEducation` table)
- Multiple entries:
  - Education Level (High School / Intermediate / Graduate / Post Graduate / PhD)
  - Institute Name, Location, Stream/Subject
  - Pass Year, Marks Details (%), Medium (Hindi/English/Other)
  - Document Image URL
- Backend: `employee_education` table (JSONB or relational)

### 2d. Contact Info Section
- Primary Phone, Alternate Phone (optional), Email (optional)
- Address (multiple: Permanent + Temporary)

