## 3. Space Management System

### 3a. Database Tables (New)
```sql
-- Space categories (classrooms, offices, store rooms are default, non-deletable)
CREATE TABLE space_categories (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  school_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  is_default BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  UNIQUE(school_id, name)
);

-- Spaces (each physical area)
CREATE TABLE spaces (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  space_id VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,   -- auto: SP001
  school_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  space_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  space_category VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,    -- classroom, office, store room, etc.
  space_number VARCHAR(50),                -- auto-assigned classroom number
  capacity INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  data JSONB DEFAULT '{}'
);

-- Materials per space
CREATE TABLE space_materials (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  school_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  space_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  material_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  quantity INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  unit VARCHAR(50)                         -- chairs, benches, tables, markers, etc.
);

-- Employees assigned to spaces
CREATE TABLE space_employees (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  school_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  space_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  employee_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  UNIQUE(school_id, space_id, employee_id)
);
```

### 3b. Backend Routes ([routes/spaces.rs](file:///home/shivnk/.gemini/antigravity/playground/deep-helix/Ai-school/Backend/src/routes/spaces.rs) — extend)
- `GET /api/spaces/:schoolId` — list all spaces
- `POST /api/spaces/:schoolId` — create space (auto-assign space_id, space_number)
- `GET /api/spaces/:schoolId/:spaceId` — space details + employees + materials + responsibilities
- `POST /api/spaces/:schoolId/:spaceId/materials` — add/update materials
- `POST /api/spaces/:schoolId/:spaceId/employees` — assign employee to space
- `DELETE /api/spaces/:schoolId/:spaceId/employees/:empId` — remove from space
- `GET /api/spaces/:schoolId/categories` — list categories
- `POST /api/spaces/:schoolId/categories` — create new category (not allowed to delete defaults)

### 3c. Frontend (New `SpaceManagement` component)
- List all spaces with category, capacity, employee count
- Create new space: select category → auto-fills space type restrictions (classroom only in classroom category)
- Space detail view: shows employees, materials, responsibilities

