## 4. Responsibility System (Enhanced)

### 4a. Enhanced [responsibilities](file:///home/shivnk/.gemini/antigravity/playground/deep-helix/Ai-school/Backend/src/repository/postgres.rs#2035-2061) table
Add columns:
```sql
ALTER TABLE responsibilities ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS
  work_level VARCHAR(50),         -- fresher, junior, experienced
  work_amount DECIMAL(12,2),
  work_period VARCHAR(50),        -- per_day, per_week, per_month, per_year, custom
  custom_dates JSONB,             -- for custom period
  total_price DECIMAL(12,2);

-- Link responsibilities to multiple spaces
CREATE TABLE responsibility_spaces (
  responsibility_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  school_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  space_id VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (responsibility_id, space_id)
);
```

### 4b. Create Responsibility flow
- Name, description
- Choose spaces: by space category OR specific space IDs (multiple)
- Work level: Fresher / Junior / Experienced
- Work amount + period (per day / per week / per month / per year / custom dates)
- Set total price (rate for this responsibility)

### 4c. Assign Responsibility to Employee
- Select employee → select multiple spaces → select responsibilities per space
- System validates: is employee already assigned to this space?

---

## 5. Salary Calculation Engine

### Formula
```
Monthly Salary =
  Σ (spaces × responsibility_rate)         [for each responsibility across all spaces]
  + experience_years × experience_rate     [configurable per profile type]
  + tenure_months × tenure_rate            [configurable]
  + bonus                                  [ad-hoc, configurable per employee]
  + AID (Additional Incentive)             [when education > experience or vice versa]
  – deductions                             [unauthorized absent days]
```

### Deductions
- `daily_rate = monthly_salary / 30`
- `deduction = unauthorized_absent_days × daily_rate`
- Customizable %: e.g., deduct only 10% of daily rate per absent day

### Backend ([emppay.rs](file:///home/shivnk/.gemini/antigravity/playground/deep-helix/Ai-school/Backend/src/routes/emppay.rs) — extend)
- `GET /api/employees/:schoolId/:empId/salary-breakdown` — full breakdown
- `POST /api/employees/:schoolId/:empId/bonus` — add one-time bonus
- `POST /api/employees/:schoolId/:empId/aid` — add Additional Incentive/Deduction
- `GET /api/employees/:schoolId/salary-params` — school-level rate config

### Frontend (`SalaryBreakdown` component)
- Card showing: base from responsibilities, experience component, tenure component, bonus, AID
- Total monthly salary clearly shown

